2026-03-07 14:07:19 - aiosqlite - DEBUG - executing functools.partial(<built-in method execute of sqlite3.Connection object at 0x0000020595C11990>, 'INSERT INTO library_documents \n                (id, category, name, icon, description, content, tags, agents, created_at, updated_at)\n                VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)', ('b0afccd2-bf1a-4f23-87fd-a60e9eee3dd0', 'libraries', 'datetime', '📅', 'Manipulation dates/heures Python — datetime, timedelta, isoformat', '# datetime — Référence rapide\n\n## Maintenant\nfrom datetime import datetime, timedelta\n\nnow = datetime.now()\ntoday = datetime.today()\nutc_now = datetime.utcnow()\n\n## Créer une date\ndt = datetime(2024, 3, 5, 14, 30, 0)\n\n## Formater\niso = dt.isoformat()  # "2024-03-05T14:30:00"\nformatted = dt.strftime("%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S")\n\n## Parser\ndt = datetime.fromisoformat("2024-03-05T14:30:00")\ndt = datetime.strptime("2024-03-05", "%Y-%m-%d")\n\n## Calculs\ntomorrow = now + timedelta(days=1)\nlast_week = now - timedelta(weeks=1)\nin_2_hours = now + timedelta(hours=2)\n\n## Comparaisons\nif dt1 > dt2:\n    print("dt1 est après dt2")\n\ndiff = dt1 - dt2  # timedelta\ndays_diff = diff.days\nseconds_diff = diff.total_seconds()', '["python", "time", "dates"]', '["CODEUR"]', '2026-03-07T14:07:19.839276', '2026-03-07T14:07:19.839276'))
2026-03-07 14:07:19 - aiosqlite - DEBUG - operation functools.partial(<built-in method execute of sqlite3.Connection object at 0x0000020595C11990>, 'INSERT INTO library_documents \n                (id, category, name, icon, description, content, tags, agents, created_at, updated_at)\n                VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)', ('b0afccd2-bf1a-4f23-87fd-a60e9eee3dd0', 'libraries', 'datetime', '📅', 'Manipulation dates/heures Python — datetime, timedelta, isoformat', '# datetime — Référence rapide\n\n## Maintenant\nfrom datetime import datetime, timedelta\n\nnow = datetime.now()\ntoday = datetime.today()\nutc_now = datetime.utcnow()\n\n## Créer une date\ndt = datetime(2024, 3, 5, 14, 30, 0)\n\n## Formater\niso = dt.isoformat()  # "2024-03-05T14:30:00"\nformatted = dt.strftime("%Y-%m-%d %H:%M:%S")\n\n## Parser\ndt = datetime.fromisoformat("2024-03-05T14:30:00")\ndt = datetime.strptime("2024-03-05", "%Y-%m-%d")\n\n## Calculs\ntomorrow = now + timedelta(days=1)\nlast_week = now - timedelta(weeks=1)\nin_2_hours = now + timedelta(hours=2)\n\n## Comparaisons\nif dt1 > dt2:\n    print("dt1 est après dt2")\n\ndiff = dt1 - dt2  # timedelta\ndays_diff = diff.days\nseconds_diff = diff.total_seconds()', '["python", "time", "dates"]', '["CODEUR"]', '2026-03-07T14:07:19.839276', '2026-03-07T14:07:19.839276')) completed
