2026-03-07 14:07:19 - aiosqlite - DEBUG - executing functools.partial(<built-in method execute of sqlite3.Connection object at 0x0000020595C11990>, 'INSERT INTO library_documents \n                (id, category, name, icon, description, content, tags, agents, created_at, updated_at)\n                VALUES (?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?, ?)', ('4bef19bd-70bb-4fdd-ab03-6d7760c8d2dd', 'libraries', 'uuid', '🔑', "Génération d'identifiants uniques — uuid4, str(uuid)", '# uuid — Référence rapide\n\n## Générer un UUID\nimport uuid\n\n# UUID v4 (aléatoire)\nid = uuid.uuid4()\nprint(id)  # UUID(\'...\')\nprint(str(id))  # string\n\n## Utilisation typique\nfrom datetime import datetime\n\ndef create_user(name):\n    return {\n        "id": str(uuid.uuid4()),\n        "name": name,\n        "created_at": datetime.now().isoformat()\n    }\n\n## UUID v3/v5 (basé sur namespace + nom)\nnamespace = uuid.NAMESPACE_DNS\nid = uuid.uuid5(namespace, "example.com")\n# Toujours le même UUID pour le même input', '["python", "id", "unique"]', '["CODEUR"]', '2026-03-07T14:07:19.996871', '2026-03-07T14:07:19.996871'))
